   <topic>BACKUP_DATABASE Function</topic>
   <syntax>C Backup_Database()</syntax>
   <description>Brings up the Backup Database dialog so that you can backup the current database.</description>
   <discussion>
BACKUP_DATABASE() displays the Backup Database dialog, allowing you to make a backup copy of the current database.

   </discussion>
